originalText.text: I have been working with Sabina for over four years to treat various ailments. Before Sabina, I had never tried acupuncture and she was excellent at educating me and making me feel comfortable. She is extremely patient and attentive, and customizes each treatment to how I'm feeling and what my body needs that day. She's skilled in a variety of complimentary modalities to provide holistic care. She's been able to help my body heal from orthopedic surgeries, and manage stress and anxiety. And, she's super fun to work with! I cannot recommend Sabina enough to help with any physical or mental care.

originalText.text: I was referred to New Horizons Acupuncture (Sabina Maez) by a colleague of mine and I am so thankful to have found her!!! I have been seeing Sabina once a week for about 6 months to treat a running related injury.  Prior to visiting Sabina, I had never done acupuncture but now I am a true convert.  Not only has Sabina helped me with my injury, she has become my go-to for healing on other fronts as well - immunity, mind/body balance, and overall stress management.  She is a true professional - attentive, experienced and a very good listener.  I am very lucky to have found her and I will continue to see her on a regular basis even now that I am back to running again.

originalText.text: I'm so grateful that I was referred to Sabina by a friend of mine. I've gone to Sabina many times to help treat various pains and issues with my alignment. Not only is she incredibly knowledgeable and kind, as a dancer, I specifically appreciate her willingness to explain her process and answer all of my questions. Sessions with her include acupuncture and many other methods resulting in a very extensive and thoughtful course of care! In addition to alleviating physical pains, I always leave feeling more balanced and at ease. I highly recommend her!

originalText.text:
Sabina has been my acupuncturist for close to three years.  Her care and attention to my well being, which translates in treatments that are focused on what is causing me pain or discomfort, has been why I’ve been and will be a long time supporter.

Her techniques are innovative and effective.  Each sessions starts with questions about how I feel and what is affecting me.  Questions reveal things that I don’t think about or connect.  Sabina is making these observations and connections and as a result I walk out of her practice feeling healed, relaxed and invigorated!

originalText.text: I'd had a negative experience with acupuncture several years ago and was hesitant to try it when Sabina was recommended to me for knee pain. But she convinced me to give it another try and I'm so glad she did! She's very interactive and worked with me to increase my comfort level.  Not only has she helped with knee pain, but with allergies, fatigue, and stress. I really miss it the weeks that I don't see her for treatment!
